question: Which fast food restaurant is available when approaching Heritage Park, Napa, CA within 90 kilometers from Bowditch Middle School Auditorium, Foster City, CA?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-122.248613 37.559053)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-122.287873 38.300572)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'fast_food'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-122.248613 37.559053)',4326)::geography, 90000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-122.248613 37.559053)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);

answers.poi_name: Ronald V. Dellums Federal Building Cafeteria

[3].display_name: Bowditch Middle School Auditorium, Foster City, CA
